{"tid":1426137,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"罷交差餉法律講解 from TG","createTime":"2019-08-07T00:58:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T13:12:55.000Z","uid":90017,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"92489903dbeceea5700bd5ed130dc5398cf153a2","tid":1426137,"uid":90017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:58:15.000Z","msg":"罷交差餉法律講解<br />\n<br />\n政府追收差餉，係出咗10%罰款之後仲唔交先可以追<br />\n當季如果有欠差餉，唔理金額多少都要追，與其每次交少少，不如索性唔交<br />\n<br />\n追收差餉過程繁複，要先開檔案出警告信，再唔交就排期上SCT，仲唔交就上庭判決，但法庭無權逼你交，唔交只係民事<br />\n<br />\n你繼續唔交就會釘契<br />\n釘契要搞好耐，就算釘咗契，只要你唔係賣出物業，對你係毫無影響<br />\n就算要賣出物業，只要買家同意，釘契物業都可以賣出<br />\n<br />\n政府追你唔交佢都好麻煩<br />\n如果人人都唔追，政府追一世都追唔完<br />\n<br />\n爭政府錢係民事<br />\n大家可以考慮罷交所有政府款項<br />\n<br />\n差餉物業估價署職員上<br />\n<br />\n@hkwarroom<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkwarroom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkwarroom&d=QE5rvD4iboeChbAAuj3apGL0CtalYwMF7My3GtbBKd0%3D&h=a14ef9bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkwarroom</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家一齊探討下可行性<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac51d5ca1057e9ead3edf37bd44ff3b0f20012a7","tid":1426137,"uid":222190,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:02:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j6XCdg0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj6XCdg0.png&h=c14b9380&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MqEQyg2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMqEQyg2.png&h=5d444a56&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/07/090214_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F07%2F090214_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png&h=bbc652e2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/07/090217_0f6641dea7107721bd03942237f5fc64.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/t